  "instructions": [
    "Drain and rinse the cannellini beans and place them in a bowl.",
    "Heat a skillet over medium heat and sear the diced pork belly until crisp, about 4 minutes.",
    "Add the seared pork to the beans and toss to combine.",
    "Stir in the halved cherry tomatoes, sliced onion, olive oil, and red wine vinegar.",
    "Season with fish sauce, dill, salt, and black pepper, then mix thoroughly.",
    "Let the salad sit for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve immediately as a light lunch dish."
